WEBVTT

00:00:57.292 --> 00:01:00.393
made up of an individual
that started life as one sex

00:01:00.417 --> 00:01:02.434
and transitioned to another.

00:01:02.458 --> 00:01:04.059
Oysters?

00:01:04.083 --> 00:01:05.518
Grouper?

00:01:05.542 --> 00:01:07.268
Shrimp?

00:01:07.292 --> 00:01:09.768
Seeing some heads nodding, yeah.

00:01:09.792 --> 00:01:13.792
But not all fish that change sex
start as females.

00:01:14.667 --> 00:01:17.476
Those clown fish we know
from "Finding Nemo"?

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.417
They're all born male.

00:01:20.042 --> 00:01:23.434
So in the real world,

00:01:23.458 --> 00:01:26.143
when Nemo's mother died,

00:01:26.167 --> 00:01:30.476
Nemo's dad Marlin
would have transitioned into Marlene --